title: T20 World Cup - Semi-finalists confirmed, so who reaches the final?
description: Nasser and Athers are up at the crack of dawn to make a flight to Guyana, after the World Cup semi-finalists are confirmed.They discuss the culmination of the Super 8s, look ahead to the match ups in the last four and reveal who they think will make the final on Saturday.
author: Sky Sports
